OL,3,CMore than 1.5 million older people
OL,4,Ccould face Christmas alone
OL,6,FAmbassador Dame Joanna Lumley
OL,7,Fdescribes this as a "crisis hidden in
OL,8,Fplain sight."
OL,10,FThe actor and campaigner warned that
OL,11,F"silence can be deafening" for older
OL,12,Fpeople who are socially isolated,
OL,13,Fparticularly during the festive period.
OL,15,FDame Joanna is joining a host of
OL,16,Ffamous faces, including Brian Cox,
OL,17,FDame Judi Dench and Miriam Margolyes,
OL,18,Fto encourage people to support Age
OL,19,FUK's campaign to provide companionship
OL,20,Fto help tackle loneliness.
