OL,3,CMore than 1.5 million older people
OL,4,Ccould face Christmas alone
OL,6,FDame Judi said, "For so many older
OL,7,Fpeople, it (Christmas) can be a time
OL,8,Fof silence ` days without conversation
OL,9,For company".
OL,11,FWhile Succession star Brian Cox said
OL,12,Fthat loneliness at Christmas is "a
OL,13,Ftragedy we don't talk about enough",
OL,14,Fwith "far too many older people are
OL,15,Fleft spending the season in silence,
OL,16,Fwhen it should be a time of warmth,
OL,17,Fconnection and joy".
