OL,3,CMore than 1.5 million older people
OL,4,Ccould face Christmas alone
OL,6,FEchoing the same sentiment, actor
OL,7,FMiriam Margolyes says that "Growing
OL,8,Folder shouldn't mean disappearing into
OL,9,Fthe background, we need to be seen,
OL,10,Fheard and celebrated."
OL,12,FAge UK says its volunteers made more
OL,13,Fthan 70,000 minutes' worth of calls to
OL,14,Fpeople during the Christmas week last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FIt regularly supports events,
OL,18,Fincluding coffee mornings or, at this
OL,19,Ftime of year, festive lunches, to
OL,20,Fensure people have the chance to
OL,21,Finteract in person.
